  <steps>
    <step num="0">Combine the chicken with the other ingredients. </step>
    <step num="1">Marinate for 2-10 hours. </step>
    <step num="2">Fry all sides of the chicken drumsticks in a frying pan over a medium heat until the skin turns golden brown. </step>
    <step num="3">Pour the marinade in the pan, put the lid on and simmer for 20 minutes. </step>
    <step num="4">Turn the chicken and simmer with the lid off for another 20 minutes. </step>
    <step num="5">Serve. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
